(G–I), dissected adult, photo images: A—lamellar seta and partially lamellar and sublamellar lines, anterolateral view; B—right genital plate; C—rostrum, dorsal view; D—inner rostral tooth; E—anterior dentate margin of ventral plate; F— tuberculate sculpturing of leg trochanter IV; G—striate and tuberculate sculpturing of anterior part of pteromorph; H—striate and tuberculate sculpturing of lateral part of pteromorph; I—adanal lyrifissure.
</paragraph>
